{"tid":1569011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我認為需要 組織返一套作戰指令","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T13:23:04.000Z","uid":34145,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5020ad9e7e8cfd2bd827d1766bf5764726be7c","tid":1569011,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"揾啲特定嘅標誌配對返 一啲現場嘅行動<br />\n<br />\n基本嘅要有 集合，散開，前進，後退，預備 等等指令<br />\n<br />\n而且要分配角色， 1組人 入面邊個攻 邊個補位都要有。<br />\n<br />\n重點要救手足"},{"pid":"187f0c4c82d9946d7ba6dc7844531c13c761d1b8","tid":1569011,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad5cd1ebdbf39555614465cd5129a049677ff872","tid":1569011,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:55:36.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"4e2ce41389a6639454ca824001714f67fd308ee7","tid":1569011,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:56:34.000Z","msg":"驚黑警用呢套方法控制返前線"},{"pid":"e2bd5fb5b2ac8c9a33f786a7740a18d09b63a51e","tid":1569011,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e2ce41389a6639454ca824001714f67fd308ee7","tid":1569011,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:56:34.000Z","msg":"驚黑警用呢套方法控制返前線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"實在滲透到入嚟都冇辦法<br />\n但係前線手足會分到幾時會做咩嘅<br />\n加啲指令集方便組織行動 一氣呵成<br />\n<br />\n同埋有時 要凝聚到分區嘅手足<br />\n被人街邊打到埋身 就因為得自己一個唔敢還手<br />\n有時 得2個 普通狗捉到人<br />\n大家都有意識埋去 撞開佢地/打狗棍嘅話<br />\n會救到多啲手足"}]}